<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183158>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Dorsolateral and ventral views of living holotype of Osornophryne puruanta (QCAZ 11471, SVL 41.3 mm), adult female collected near Laguna Puruanta at 3000 m. a. s. l., Cordillera de Pimampiro, Provincia de Imbabura, Ecuador. Photographs by Luis Coloma." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183158/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183159>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dorsal (A) and lateral (B) views of the head (QCAZ 7685) and ventral views of palmer (C) and plantar (D) surfaces of Osornophryne puruanta (EPN 7083). Scale = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183159/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183161>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dorsal (A) and lateral (B) views of the head (QCAZ 14082 and QCAZ 14080, respectively) and ventral views of palmar (C) and plantar (D) surfaces (QCAZ 14080 and QCAZ 14082, respectively) of O. bufoniformis. Scale = 2 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183161/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183162>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Dorsal views of vertebral column (A) and hand (B) of Osornophryne puruanta (QCAZ 13320, adult female)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183162/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183163>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Schematic map showing the known distribution of species in the genus Osornophryne." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183163/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

